OL,3,CMurder probe after Brighton double
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after one man died and
OL,8,Fanother suffered serious injuries
OL,9,Fduring a fight in Brighton.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to a property in
OL,12,FRegency Square at around 2.10am on
OL,13,FSunday, April 26, following reports of
OL,14,Fa disturbance.
OL,16,FInside, two men were found with stab
OL,17,Finjuries. One victim, in his 30s, was
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital in a serious
OL,19,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
