OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777295491
OL,3,CMurder probe after Brighton double
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FThe second man, aged 37, was
OL,7,Fpronounced dead at the scene a short
OL,8,Fwhile later. His family been informed.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Sussex Police said a
OL,11,F26 year old man, of no fixed address,
OL,12,Fwas arrested at a nearby location
OL,14,FHe is currently in custody being
OL,15,Fquestioned on suspicion of murder,
OL,16,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent, and
OL,17,Fpossession of a Class A drug with
OL,18,Fintent to supply.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
