OL,3,CMurder probe after Brighton double
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FBrighton Chief Superintendent, Adam
OL,7,FHays, said; "This incident has had
OL,8,Fdevastating consequences, resulting in
OL,9,Fthe loss of one man's life and leaving
OL,10,Fanother with serious injuries.
OL,12,F"There is not believed to be a wider
OL,13,Frisk to the public, and a thorough
OL,14,Finvestigation is underway to establish
OL,15,Fthe full circumstances.
OL,17,F"As this continues, there will be an
OL,18,Fincreased police presence in and
OL,19,Faround Regency Square.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
