OL,3,CMurder probe after Brighton double
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,F"We are committed to robustly tackling
OL,7,Fknife crime and will take swift and
OL,8,Fdecisive action against those involved
OL,9,Fin violent offending in Brighton."
